    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2 class="legal-block__title">What We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect the following information when you interact with Almost Human Group:</p>
      <ul class="legal-block__list">
        <li><strong>Name and email address</strong> &mdash; when you fill out a contact form, sign up for our newsletter, join the waitlist, or become a member.</li>
        <li><strong>Organization name</strong> &mdash; when optionally provided through contact or partnership forms.</li>
        <li><strong>Payment information</strong> &mdash; when you become a Founding Member or paid member. Payment processing is handled entirely by Stripe. We do not store your credit card number, CVV, or full payment details on our servers.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage data</strong> &mdash; basic analytics about how you use our website (pages visited, time on site). We do not use third-party tracking pixels or sell this data.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2 class="legal-block__title">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul class="legal-block__list">
        <li><strong>Communication</strong> &mdash; to respond to your inquiries, send newsletter updates, and provide membership information.</li>
        <li><strong>Membership management</strong> &mdash; to process payments, manage your membership status, and deliver member benefits.</li>
        <li><strong>Advocacy and organizing</strong> &mdash; to coordinate volunteers, mobilize supporters, and advance our mission as a 501(c)(4) social welfare organization.</li>
        <li><strong>Improving our work</strong> &mdash; to understand how people engage with our programs and organization so we can serve them better.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2 class="legal-block__title">We Do Not Sell Your Data</h2>
      <p>Almost Human Group will never sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties. Period. Your information is used solely for the purposes described above. We may share data with service providers (such as Stripe for payment processing and email delivery services) only as necessary to operate our programs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2 class="legal-block__title">Cookies</h2>
      <p>Our website uses essential cookies to maintain your session and ensure the site functions properly. We do not use advertising cookies or third-party tracking cookies. Essential cookies are necessary for features like form submissions and member login sessions. By using our website, you consent to the use of these essential cookies.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2 class="legal-block__title">Data Security</h2>
      <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information, including encryption in transit (HTTPS), secure password hashing for admin accounts, and access controls limiting who can view personal data. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2 class="legal-block__title">Updating or Deleting Your Information</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul class="legal-block__list">
        <li>Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</li>
        <li>Request corrections to inaccurate information.</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your personal data.</li>
        <li>Unsubscribe from our newsletter at any time.</li>
        <li>Cancel your membership and stop recurring payments.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To make any of these requests, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@almosthumangroup.org">hello@almosthumangroup.org</a>. We will respond within 30 days.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="legal-block">
      <h2 class="legal-block__title">Changes to This Policy</h2>
